data.description: Welcome to this cute and cozy home.   Perfect for the first-time homebuyer, empty nesters, or for the investor.   Split floor plan with 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms.  Roof and gutters in 2021/2022, Water heater and HVAC approximately 6 years old. Updated Kitchen with granite counter tops.   Both bathrooms have updated tile work in the tub/shower.   Detached Barn style storage shed (2014) in the backyard, great for man cave, she-shed, or just for storage. Great location, within walking distance to Dave's Oyster Bar, and a short drive to the shopping centers, restaurants and to beautiful beaches.
